rows.label: qst105406_msg0002
rows.name:
You must have toiled a great deal to
locate all four treasures!

rows.label: qst105406_msg0003
rows.name: Heh... All in a day's work, I guess?

rows.label: qst105406_msg0004
rows.name:
Rex, I hereby anoint you...Salvager
Supreme!

rows.label: qst105406_msg0006
rows.name:
Ah, forgive me. I acknowledge it is a
somewhat old-fashioned title for
a youngster such as you.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0007
rows.name:
No no, I like it! Really! It's got a nice
ring to it!

rows.label: qst105406_msg0008
rows.name:
Salvager Supreme... A salvager
among salvagers...

rows.label: qst105406_msg0010
rows.name:
It is I who should be thanking you, Rex,
for fulfilling an old man's dream.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0011
rows.name:
It is not just the title you have earned,
but my deepest respect. It is only fitting
that you receive an ample reward.

rows.label: qst105406_msg0101
rows.name:
I see you've gathered all four
treasures. Would you mind letting
me speak to Rex?
